Name: Moves
About the game: This game has great inspiration in the game qop. Moves is a minimalist puzzle game where you must use your mathematical skills to solve tricky puzzles. Collect the right numbers and operations to make progress. - FullHD - 40 achievements - 40 levels (from simple to insufferably difficult) - Smooth animation Controls: WASD or ARROWS Restart level: R
